description:
First amazing Volume. It all starts here!!

Space Coast Comixx is Central Florida's premier magazine. You can find the magazine distributed throughout Central Florida, along with issues in Chicago and many other areas. Plus it is the first appearance of the Demon in a Spacesuit.

This series had five issues, then it is followed by second volume, before a third volume returns the series to it's original numbering.
name: Space Coast Comixx

deck: This is the first amazing issue of The Unbelievable Detergent Man.
description:
Jose Mesarina who is better known as Nino Mesarina is the creator of the Unbelievable Laundry Detergent Man. The original series which consist of four issues was printed with Instant Press, a small outfit out in Chicago. Below is the first four issues, which were printed in black and white, and on newsprint paper.

An unlikely hero enters the world of crime fighting!

WARNING: Drinking Soap Will Kill You!

These four issues explain the characters exploits as a hero. Then shorter stories appear in many other titles. More recently many short stories in full color have appeared in Space Coast Comixx.
name: The Unbelievable Laundry Detergent Man
